               </msIdentifier>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>Psalter. At the outset is a chart with the 12 months of the year, arranged by two months at a time: Maskaram and Magabit, teqmt and Yakatit, etc., i.e., month 1 and 7, 2, and 8, etc. The ends of almost every line contains a few words of commentary on the text. Psalm 77 does not mark the midpoint. Psalm 151 is the long version. Song of Songs is the common version, but there are many, many notes throughout. There are authentic illuminations</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <textLang/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
